{
  "stem": "11133.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Of course, at that point, everything was left behind.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The only thing that we had on were the clothes on our backs, you know.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So no possessions at all.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We, you know, we lived in barracks, five to a berth.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "That was it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But for a while there, you know, we were able to walk out of the Plaszow camp and walk about-- I think the trip took about 90 minutes each way to our-- to the factory, to Madritsch factory.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "The factory was moved really from-- the factory had been moved originally, I think, from middle of Krakow to Podgorze, which is kind of a little suburb over the bridge, of the-- Vistula bridge.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And Madritsch established a factory there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And we walked from Plaszow to this factory every day, and walked back.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We were not as fortunate as the Schindler people, who were able to stay and live at the factory.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "We had to live in the barracks.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "You know that Plaszow, the camp, was made originally on the Jewish cemetery.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So they crushed the stones.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "So we walked every day over people's names, you know.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "So that was kind of humiliating, too-- especially to people who had, you know, relatives buried at that cemetery.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "That was the largest Jewish cemetery in Krakow.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They were pretty primitive.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, all we had were the barracks.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And you know, Poland gets very, very cold in the winter, so we shivered.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We were expected-- every morning, early in the morning, we were called to the appelplatz, which was a counting place where they, you know, lined us up in fives and counted us.",
      "word_count": 32
    }
  ],
